楷体;font-size:16px\">/L。骨髓细胞学检查:增生活跃。红系增生为主，中、晚幼红比值增高，成熟红细胞大小不均，以小细胞为主，中心淡染区扩大。首选的治疗是&nbsp;</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">青年女性，既往月经量多。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">骨髓象增生活跃或明显活跃</span>;以红系增生为主,粒系、巨核系无明显异常;红系中以中、晚幼红细胞为主,其体积小、核染色质致密、胞质少、边缘不整齐,有血红蛋白形成不良的表现，即所谓的“核老浆幼”现象。提示缺铁性贫血。首选病因治疗和口服铁剂。</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">补充维生素</span>B</span><sub><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:sub\">12</span></sub><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">、叶酸</span>→巨幼细胞性贫血。口服雄性激素→慢性再障。口服泼尼松→溶血性贫血。输注红细胞→急性失血患者。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6422,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:58:41","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:58:41","isTrue":true,"questionId":2427,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">口服铁剂</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6423,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:58:41","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:58:41","isTrue":false,"questionId":2427,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">补充维生素</span>B</span><sub><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:sub\">12</span></sub><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">、叶酸</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6424,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:58:41","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:58:41","isTrue":false,"questionId":2427,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">口服雄性激素</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6425,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:58:41","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:58:41","isTrue":false,"questionId":2427,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">口服