:血红蛋白＜110g/L、中性粒细胞＜1.5×10</span><sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:super\">9</span></sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">/L、血小板＜100×10</span><sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:super\">9</span></sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">/L。骨髓增生度多在活跃以上，少部分呈增生减低。MDS患者的病态造血。②细胞遗传学改变：40%-70%的MDS有克隆性染色体核型异常,多为缺失性改变,以+8、-5/5q-、-7/7q-、20q-最为常见。（5）慢性病性贫血：慢性炎症、感染或肿瘤等引起的铁代谢异常性贫血。贫血为小细胞性。贮铁(血清铁蛋白和骨髓小粒含铁血黄素)增多。血清铁、血清铁饱和度、总铁结合力减低。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6142,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","isTrue":false,"questionId":2371,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">地中海贫血</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6143,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","isTrue":false,"questionId":2371,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">慢性病性贫血</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6144,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","isTrue":false,"questionId":2371,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">巨幼细胞贫血</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6145,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","isTrue":false,"questionId":2371,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">骨髓增生异常综合征</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6146,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","updateTime":"2019-06-20 09:36:48","isTrue":true,"questionId":2371,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">缺铁性贫血</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":954,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:32:44","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:32:44","name":"血液A2","questionCnt":10,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":1886,"createTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","topicId":null,"tagId":931,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":89,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">男，</span>50岁。拟行骨髓移植入院。血液不足，需要其亲属献血给患者用，兄妹各献血400ml，血液检测合格，患者输注。此时应对这两袋血液采取的措施是</span></p><p><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">解析：辐照血液成分</span>:血液经过X射线照射后，其中的淋巴细胞被灭活，而其他血液成分仍保留活性。辐照血液用于预防输血相关移植物抗宿主病 CTA-GVHD)，其主要适应证为 TAGVHD 高危患者，如:①免疫功能低下的受血者;②欲输注来自亲属的血液，或是 HLA 配型的血小板。凡是具有淋巴细胞活性的血液成分，如红细胞、血小板和粒细胞，均需要辐照。淋巴细胞已经丧失活性的血液成分，如冰冻解冻去甘油红细胞、冰冻血浆与冷沉淀，不必辐照。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":3725,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","updateTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","isTrue":false,"questionId":1886,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">反复洗涤</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3726,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","updateTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","isTrue":true,"questionId":1886,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">射线照射</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3727,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","updateTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","isTrue":false,"questionId":1886,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">滤除白细胞</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3728,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","updateTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","isTrue":false,"questionId":1886,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">病毒灭活</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3729,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","updateTime":"2019-06-19 14:23:47","isTrue":false,"questionId":1886,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">细菌灭活</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":954,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:32:44","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:32:44","name":"血液A2","questionCnt":10,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":931,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:38","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:38","name":"161","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":1842,"createTime":"2019-06-19 11:41:11","topicId":null,"tagId":931,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":77,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">男，</span>60岁。直肠癌根治术4天，晨起时突发左下肢肿胀，左腿皮温增高。股三角区有深压痛，最有可能的诊断是左下肢</span></p><p><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">解析：</span> <span style=\"font-family:楷体\">根据急性期血栓形成的解剖部位分型</span>:①中央型，即髂-股静脉血栓形成。左侧发病多于右侧。主要表现为起病急骤，全下肢明显肿胀，患侧腘窝、股三角区有疼痛和压痛，浅静脉扩张，患肢皮温及体温均升高。②周围型，包括股静脉血栓形成及小腿深静脉血栓形成。局限于股静脉的血栓形成，主要表现为大腿肿痛，由于髂-股静脉通畅，故下肢肿胀一般并不严重。局限在小腿部的深静脉血栓形成，表现为突发小腿剧痛，患足不能着地踏平，行走时症状加重，小腿肿胀且有深压痛，做踝关节过度背屈试验可导致小腿剧痛 (Homans 征阳性)。③混合型，即全下肢深静脉血栓形成。主要表现为全下肢明显肿胀、剧痛，股三角区、腘窝、小腿肌层都可有压痛，常伴有体温升高和脉率加速(股白肿)。如病程继续进展，肢体极度肿胀，对下股动脉造成压迫以及动脉痉挛，导致下肢动脉血供障碍，出现足背动脉和胫后动脉搏动消失，进而小腿和足背往往出现水疱，皮肤温度明显降低并呈青紫色(股青肿) ，处理不及时可发生静脉性坏疽。</span></p><p><br/></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":3516,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 11:41:11","updateTime":"2019-06-19 11:41:11","isTrue":false,"questionId":1842,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">淋巴水肿</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":3517,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 11:41:11","updateTime":"2019-06-19 11:41:11","isTrue":false,"questionId":1842,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">血栓性浅静脉炎</span></span></p>","sel